data.description: Welcome to this beautiful Tudor-style home in the historic landmark of Addisleigh Park. This home was updated in 2020 and features a live fireplace on the first floor, four bedrooms, three full bathrooms, and a finished basement. The home has a private driveway and a spacious lot of 4,000 sqft. The home is conveniently located near public transportation, schools, and shopping. This home is a rare gem in the neighborhood and is ready for you to move in and enjoy. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of history in Addisleigh Park!
